{"tid":2421657,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"深水埗男子公廁遭兩刀煞封嘴綁劫　失逾萬元掙扎求救","createTime":"2021-02-24T15:52:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-24T17:40:45.000Z","uid":242537,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7a64a724cd477d2255cced9deb9152ba3b5c79f5","tid":2421657,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T15:52:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20210224/bkn-20210224204828933-0224_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20210224%2Fbkn-20210224204828933-0224_00822_001.html&d=s5X1yiNR%2BigbIA3iGijs8DRqNRg6ChYs1Sy50pDDGUM%3D&h=7d729291\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20210224/bkn-20210224204828933-0224_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tv.on.cc/hk/index.html?i=ONS210224-14079-59-M&amp;d=1614174535\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftv.on.cc%2Fhk%2Findex.html%3Fi%3DONS210224-14079-59-M%26d%3D1614174535&d=s5X1yiNR%2BigbIA3iGijs8DRqNRg6ChYs1Sy50pDDGUM%3D&h=cb49acf0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tv.on.cc/hk/index.html?i=ONS210224-14079-59-M&amp;d=1614174535</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20210224/photo/bkn-20210224204828933-0224_00822_001_01p.jpg?20210224225817\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20210224%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20210224204828933-0224_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20210224225817&h=68e5bdd6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n事主在公廁被歹徒綁劫，警員在場調查。(劉子文攝)。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20210224/photo/bkn-20210224204828933-0224_00822_001_02p.jpg?20210224225817\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20210224%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20210224204828933-0224_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20210224225817&h=30fb14fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n探員檢走證物。(劉子文攝)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20210224/photo/bkn-20210224204828933-0224_00822_001_03p.jpg?20210224225817\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20210224%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20210224204828933-0224_00822_001_03p.jpg%3F20210224225817&h=b1de71d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n事主被推入廁格劫財。(劉子文攝)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20210224/photo/bkn-20210224204828933-0224_00822_001_04p.jpg?20210224225817\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20210224%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20210224204828933-0224_00822_001_04p.jpg%3F20210224225817&h=80c646ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警方封鎖現場調查。(劉子文攝)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20210224/photo/bkn-20210224204828933-0224_00822_001_05p.jpg?20210224225817\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20210224%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20210224204828933-0224_00822_001_05p.jpg%3F20210224225817&h=01e32389&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n事發現場為楓樹街遊樂場。(劉子文攝)<br />\n<br />\n深水埗發生行劫案，今晚(24日)7時許，一名姓梁(57歲)男子在楓樹街遊樂場公廁如廁時，突有2名大約30多歲的外籍男子趨近，將他推入廁格並亮出生果刀指嚇，低聲威脅他不得聲張。梁怯於刀鋒不敢反抗，隨即被對方用索帶綑綁四肢及以牛皮膠紙封嘴，歹徒之後搜索梁的財物，掠走其隨身袋內約13,000港元現金及手機後，拋下他飛奔而去。<br />\n<br />\n梁為了求救，活動受制下只好「半行半跳」掙扎離開公廁，他勉強走至汝州街及黃竹街交界時，一名駕車駛經現場之的哥發現梁的窘境，立即落車為他鬆綁及協助報警。警方接報趕至封鎖現場調查，梁幸無受傷，向警員講述事發經過，其後隨同登上警車在附近兜截賊人，惟經搜索後未有發現，警方正追查涉案歹徒身份及下落。"},{"pid":"f6a58ce8b712e54ebbb432e16884d5714376507b","tid":2421657,"uid":242537,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T15:52:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fc7604369dca2549ff8a96aa22bab9a43a493c6","tid":2421657,"uid":204539,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T15:57:14.000Z